Prime Cabinet Secretary Musalia Mudavadi on Monday condoled with the late Education CS George Magoha 's family. Mudavadi eulogised Magoha as colossus in space and he took up his role with a lot of gusto. Magoha will be buried this Saturday  in Umiru, Nyamininia sub-county. The former CS , 71, passed on January 24 at the Nairobi Hospital.